<figureCitation id="1366A0DBFFF71566E67A18CEFEFF3BD3" box="[287,345,187,214]" captionStart="FIGURE 5" captionStartId="14.[151,250,1930,1954]" captionTargetBox="[172,1421,359,1891]" captionTargetId="figure-102@14.[152,1436,345,1907]" captionTargetPageId="14" captionText="FIGURE 5. A–C. Pristonesia sicril sp. nov.; D–F. Pristonesia tainatril sp. nov.; G–I. Pristonesia uvenil sp. nov.. A, D, G. Hypopygium, external view; B, E, H. Genitalia, dorsal view; C, F, I. Genitalia, ventral view. Black = cupula; dark grey = ventral valvae; light grey = apical membranous bubble. Scale bars = 100 µm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6410670" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6410670/files/figure.png" pageId="12" pageNumber="333">5G–I</figureCitation>
